  icon: {fileID: 2800000, guid: 727a75301c3d24613a3ebcec4a24c2c8, type: 3}
  title: Udder Destruction
  sections:
  - heading: Project Overview
    text: Udder Destruction is a top-down survivor-style Unity game. The player chooses one of four cows before play begins, then fights automatic waves while collecting Bovinity and power upgrades.
    linkText: 
    url:
  - heading: Player Naming Note
    text: Older notes, scene objects, prefabs, and code written before character selection may refer to Moolissa. Unless the context specifically means the Moolissa character option, treat those references as meaning the player or the currently selected cow.
    linkText: 
    url:
  - heading: Selectable Cows
    text: Moolissa starts with Beefcake level 1 and a red tint. Macowrena starts with Whole Milk level 1 and the default tint. Marge starts with Butter level 1 and a yellow tint. Hattie starts with Prion Infection level 1 and a green tint. All cows also start with Stomp level 1.
    linkText: 
    url:
  - heading: Key Scenes
    text: Primary scene: Assets/Scenes/SampleScene.unity. Test scene: Assets/Scenes/test scene.unity.
    linkText: 
    url:
  - heading: Handover
    text: See PROJECT_HANDOVER.txt for current gameplay notes, known risks, build guidance, and project-specific development rules.
    linkText: 
    url:
  loadedLayout: 1
